  "title": "Cooked Carrots",
  "description": "Just like normal carrots, but you eat them faster",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KgK7VbF.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/MarsThePlanet\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/endpoint.svg?url=https%3A%2F%2Fshieldsio-patreon.vercel.app%2Fapi%3Fusername%3DMarsThePlanet%26type%3Dpatrons&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cooked-carrots\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/615985?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cooked-carrots\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/cooked-carrots?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod adds one new item, the cooked carrot. A cooked carrot is a food item that restores the same amount of hunger and saturation as a regular carrot, but is eaten twice as fast and you can eat it even while having a full hunger bar. </p></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Eating speed of a cooked carrot compared to a regular carrot</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uiQ4ZFW.gif\" width=\"350\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pnvGogE.gif\" width=\"350\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1XaBbqr.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"190\"/>&nbsp;</p></center> \n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNZ2GMV.png\"/>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/deimos-fabric-forge-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/83sD0W8.png\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deimos\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/j2GIPnt.png\"/></a>\n</p></center> \n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/marstheplanet\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rJIRiP5.png\" /></a></p>",
